annotationA: NADH dehydrogenase (ubiquinone) activity; NADH dehydrogenase activity. It is involved in the biological process described with: oxidation-reduction process; Belongs to the complex I 30 kDa subunit family
annotationB: Component of the ubiquinol-cytochrome c reductase complex (complex III or cytochrome b-c1 complex), which is a respiratory chain that generates an electrochemical potential coupled to ATP synthesis.
